              "description": {
                "paragraph": [
                  "Now even the heaviest packages can withstand rough handling. Our Scotch Heavy Duty Shipping Packaging Tape holds strong on all box types, including 100% recycled boxes. It's even guaranteed to stay sealed. The strong, tough, solvent-free hot melt adhesive locks in your heavy duty contents and locks out everything else."
